text: Bikyan () is a rural locality (a village) in Verkhnegaleyevsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 29 as of 2010. There is 1 street.Карта Зилаирского района Башкортостана == Geography == It is located 82 km from Zilair, 7 km from Verkhnegaleyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Bikyan
